FT  28 JAN 92 / UK Company News: Bristol Channel
Bristol Channel Ship Repairers returned to the black in the 28 weeks to
October 11.
The pre-tax outcome - Pounds 74,884 against losses of Pounds 231,065 - came
on turnover of Pounds 661,801 (Pounds 548,451). Mr Chris Bailey, chairman,
expected turnover to remain at much the same level in the second half. He
anticipated ' a continued improvement in ship repairing and overall
profits'.
Earnings per share worked through at 0.09p (losses of 0.29p).
